.********************************************************************** 
.
PROC0000  CALL       CREA0000               * Create Temp File
.
          MOVE      ZERO,RECCOUNT      * zero record counter 
.
          PACK       KEY27,FROMDATE,SP30 
          CALL       RDSTREA3
PROC1000
          CALL       RDKTREA3
....  DISPLAY   *P1:3,*DBON,"PROC>",WMURNO,WMCODE,WMCNT,"|",WMSTAT,"|",WMDATE1:
....                    "|",WMUNIT,"|",WMDOCTOR,"|",WMPTY,"|"
